56
00:04:53.000 --> 00:04:59.000
Within Sequencer, these UI shortcuts will make navigating around Sequencer considerably easier.

57
00:05:02.000 --> 00:05:07.000
Right mouse button and drag will pan the timeline horizontally and vertically.

58
00:05:07.000 --> 00:05:14.000
Middle mouse button scroll will move the timeline up and down while shift and scroll will also pan the timeline left and right.

59
00:05:15.000 --> 00:05:18.000
Control and scroll is used for zooming the timeline.

60
00:05:19.000 --> 00:05:25.000
Alt-Shift, right mouse button drag can be used for free-form zooming around the time marker,

61
00:05:25.000 --> 00:05:29.000
and pressing the Home key on your keyboard will reset the range slider bounds.

62
00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:35.000
Control plus drag on the time bar to the right will define a specific zoom region,

63
00:05:35.000 --> 00:05:40.000
whereas control drag on the time bar to the left will reset the zoom region.

